{"tid":849174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《洛克人》慘遭真人化？ 福斯影業繼《七龍珠》後再次出手啦","createTime":"2018-10-05T13:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T14:06:33.000Z","uid":179810,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbbd63a6130f3478dae8e3242108c213f0baac1","tid":849174,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CD5mhOCUgAAR8KZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCD5mhOCUgAAR8KZ.jpg&h=68cf1a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">當然不是巨石強森飾演（圖片來源：NeoGAF）</span><br />\n<br />\n為了慶祝《洛克人》系列邁入30周年，卡普空（CAPCOM）正式宣佈《洛克人》系列將開拍真人電影版，由20世紀福斯（20th Century Fox）製作，由曾拍過《鬼入鏡3》的阿里爾舒曼（Ariel Schulman）與亨利喬斯特（Henry Joost）執導。<br />\n<br />\n「洛克人」系列，自1987年的第一作推出以來，全系列已經累積銷售3千2百萬套，最新作「洛克人11：命運的齒輪!!」也已經在日前上市。這個IP一路走來也在動畫、漫畫推出過作品，但看來這次卡普空認為還不夠，終於要走上真人電影化的末路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/04/99/5350067.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F99%2F5350067.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=dc49a9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡普空在官網宣佈，真人版電影開拍。<br />\n<br />\n目前電影名稱，暫定為「MEGAMAN」(美版洛克人譯名），由曾經發行過漫畫改編電影《X戰警》、《死侍》的20世紀福斯製作，並找來了雙導演組合阿里爾舒曼與亨利喬斯特，曾經拍過知名的偽紀錄恐怖片《鬼入鏡3》與《鬼入鏡4》；另外，日裔美籍的演員岡政偉將擔任監製，他曾經出演過人氣美劇《超異能英雄》（Heroes）的人氣角色「中村廣」而廣為人知，本身也是個遊戲與漫畫迷。<br />\n<br />\n其實，去年就已傳出將改編真人電影的消息，如今卡普空親自宣佈，相信這次真的要搬上大銀幕了。不過目前會以哪篇故事、世界觀做改編，或是完全的原創劇情都尚為知曉。不管如何，都希望不會又是另一次慘遭真人化，別忘了20世紀福斯也曾發行過災難般的真人電影《七龍珠：全新進化》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/04/99/5350031.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F99%2F5350031.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=e3e1baac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又一童年被毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc426ff5ac7ae54d9ba3ce6452cd8b73fcf5286e","tid":849174,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:08:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"892189b5773a5259590c557cb32501762083eb38","tid":849174,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:09:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3caa7c5e37fb0b20a393afc7bc4b8c272a98c78","tid":849174,"uid":887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"洛克人真人化都俾佢地諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9c7a2872e0e353b76645d91240c8188f2bec6d","tid":849174,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"柒到冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bad2f066981c47998fae8e910976ed8b8def4e4","tid":849174,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:11:39.000Z","msg":"一入黎見到張圖就笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641458bd71b51f37221bcc2860820a6be2e46e48","tid":849174,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/211436_e99b0ae56203c2ecc14613d9d58eabd8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F211436_e99b0ae56203c2ecc14613d9d58eabd8.jpeg&h=8fa9a2dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid